description: Dashboard for monitoring individual SFS Client nodes performance and operations

targets.expr: ((rate( request_latency_ns_count {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] ) or rate( request_latency_ms_count {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] )) or rate( sfs_rpc_response_duration_count {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] ))
targets.query: ((rate( request_latency_ns_count {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] ) or rate( request_latency_ms_count {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] )) or rate( sfs_rpc_response_duration_count {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] ))

targets.expr: ((((rate( request_latency_ns_sum {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] ) / rate( request_latency_ns_count {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] )) / 1000000) or (rate( request_latency_ms_sum {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] ) / rate( request_latency_ms_count {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] ))) or (rate( sfs_rpc_response_duration_sum {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] ) / rate( sfs_rpc_response_duration_count {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] )))
targets.query: ((((rate( request_latency_ns_sum {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] ) / rate( request_latency_ns_count {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] )) / 1000000) or (rate( request_latency_ms_sum {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] ) / rate( request_latency_ms_count {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] ))) or (rate( sfs_rpc_response_duration_sum {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] ) / rate( sfs_rpc_response_duration_count {cluster="$cluster",nsid="$nsid",job="sfs-client",instance="$node"} [$__rate_interval] )))

targets.expr: (((histogram_quantile(0.01, sum without(sfs_hostname) (rate(request_latency_ns_bucket{cluster="$cluster", nsid="$nsid", job="sfs-client", instance="$node"}[$__rate_interval]))) / 1000000) or histogram_quantile(0.01, sum without(sfs_hostname) (rate(request_latency_ms_bucket{cluster="$cluster", nsid="$nsid", job="sfs-client", instance="$node"}[$__rate_interval])))) or histogram_quantile(0.01, sum without(sfs_hostname) (rate(sfs_rpc_response_duration_bucket{cluster="$cluster", nsid="$nsid", job="sfs-client", instance="$node"}[$__rate_interval]))))
